*
*  HLQ stub
SET RULE
*  general data set protection
LIST &HLQ.
RECKEY &HLQ. ADD(- UID(-) READ(A) EXEC(P))
RECKEY &HLQ. +
ADD(- UID(&SYSPROG.) READ(A) EXEC(A) ALLOC(A) WRITE(A))
*
*  show results
LIST &HLQ.
